article.description: — Peter Kiss had 23 points and 10 rebounds as Bryant topped New Hampshire 76-59 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Kiss scores 23 to carry Bryant past New Hampshire 76-59
article.linkText: Kiss scores 23 to carry Bryant past New Hampshire 76-59
article.story: SMITHFIELD, R.I. -- — Peter Kiss had 23 points and 10 rebounds as Bryant topped New Hampshire 76-59 on Wednesday night. Adham Eleeda had 18 points and six rebounds for Bryant (4-6). Charles Pride added 16 points and 10 rebounds. Greg Calixte had nine rebounds. Jayden Martinez had 16 points for the Wildcats (4-3). Sloan Seymour added 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
